name: Fairy Tales of Geoda 02
description:
4525 x 3200px PNG 300DPI
The children of Geoda are told many tales of adventurers and warriors who roam the lands, defeating monsters and discovering the stories that came before. In this etching, the wanderer, Ceto rests for the evening regaling his traveling tales to curious animals searching for warmth. Little does he know, he's attracted quite an audience.
